<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta name="description" content="Learn how BurnLink secures your file sharing with end-to-end encryption and one-time download links." />
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#0a0a0a" />
  <title>About - BurnLink</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: "Inter", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0a0a 0%, #1a1410 100%);
      color: #ffffff;
      line-height: 1.6;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    @keyframes fadeInUp {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(40px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    @keyframes fadeInDown {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(-40px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    @keyframes slideInLeft {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateX(-60px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateX(0);
      }
    }

    header {
      padding: 2rem 0;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      background: rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.8);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.15);
      z-index: 100;
      animation: fadeInDown 0.8s ease-out;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 2rem;
    }

    .header-content {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .logo {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff8c00, #ffa500);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }

    nav a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      margin-left: 2rem;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      position: relative;
    }

    nav a:hover {
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    nav a.active {
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    nav a.active:after {
      width: 100% !important;
    }

    nav a:after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -5px;
      left: 0;
      width: 0;
      height: 2px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff8c00, #ffa500);
      transition: width 0.3s ease;
    }

    nav a:hover:after {
      width: 100%;
    }

    main {
      padding: 6rem 0;
      min-height: calc(100vh - 140px);
    }

    .about-content {
      max-width: 800px;
      animation: slideInLeft 1s ease-out;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -1.5px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff, #ff8c00);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }

    .intro {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-top: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }

    li {
      padding: 1rem 0;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
      position: relative;
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    li:hover {
      transform: translateX(10px);
    }

    li:before {
      content: "→";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      color: #ff8c00;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .features {
      background: rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.25);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 2.5rem;
      margin: 2.5rem 0;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }

    .feature-item {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.2);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .feature-item:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .feature-item:hover {
      border-color: rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.5);
      background: rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.05);
      transform: translateY(-5px);
    }

    .feature-item strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .feature-item p {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
      margin: 0;
    }

    .links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 2.5rem;
    }

    a {
      color: #ffa500;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 165, 0, 0.3);
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    a:hover {
      color: #ffffff;
      border-color: #ffa500;
      background: rgba(255, 165, 0, 0.1);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.15);
      padding: 4rem 0;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      background: rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.5);
      animation: fadeInUp 1.2s ease-out;
    }

    .footer-content {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .footer-section h3 {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .footer-section a {
      display: block;
      padding: 0;
      border: none;
      background: none;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .footer-section a:hover {
      color: #ffa500;
      transform: translateX(5px);
    }

    .footer-bottom {
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.1);
      padding-top: 2rem;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      body {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0a0a 0%, #1a1410 100%);
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 2.2rem;
      }

      h2 {
        font-size: 1.4rem;
      }

      header {
        padding: 1.5rem 0;
      }

      .container {
        padding: 0 1.5rem;
      }

      .about-content {
        padding: 0 1rem;
      }

      li {
        font-size: 1rem;
        padding: 0.75rem 0;
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
      }

      .features {
        padding: 1.5rem;
        margin: 1.5rem 0;
      }

      .feature-item {
        padding: 1rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      }

      a {
        display: block;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
      }

      .links {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
      }

      main {
        padding: 2rem 0;
      }

      footer {
        padding: 2rem 0;
      }

      .header-content {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }

      nav {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        width: 100%;
      }

      nav a {
        margin-left: 0;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }

      .footer-content {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header-content">
        <div class="logo">BurnLink</div>
        <nav>
          <a href="/">Home</a>
          <a href="/about" class="active">About</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-content">
        <h1>About BurnLink</h1>
        
        <p class="intro">BurnLink is a secure, private file sharing service that puts security and privacy at the core of every interaction. Share sensitive files with confidence knowing they're protected end-to-end.</p>

        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Files are encrypted in your browser before upload</li>
          <li>Server stores only the encrypted payload, never has access to unencrypted data</li>
          <li>Sharing links are burned after the first successful download</li>
          <li>Optional password protection with 10-minute lockout after 3 wrong attempts</li>
          <li>Zero-knowledge architecture—we can't access your files</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="features">
          <div class="feature-item">
            <strong>Privacy First</strong>
            <p>Your files are encrypted in your browser. We never see the unencrypted content.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <strong>One-Time Access</strong>
            <p>Files are deleted immediately after the first download, ensuring they're not available indefinitely.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <strong>Optional Authentication</strong>
            <p>Add password protection for additional security. Failed attempts trigger automatic lockouts.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <strong>Built for Developers</strong>
            <p>Open source, transparent, and built with privacy-conscious technology choices.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2>Why BurnLink?</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Traditional cloud storage keeps files forever</li>
          <li>Email attachments expose files through message systems</li>
          <li>Most sharing services can access your data</li>
          <li>BurnLink gives you control and privacy</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="links">
          <a href="/">← Back to Upload</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/Joy-Majumder/BurnLink" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">View on GitHub</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="footer-content">
        <div class="footer-section">
          <h3>Product</h3>
          <a href="/">Share Files</a>
          <a href="/about">How It Works</a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-section">
          <h3>Resources</h3>
          <a href="https://github.com/Joy-Majumder/BurnLink" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/Joy-Majumder/BurnLink#readme" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Documentation</a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-section">
          <h3>Developer</h3>
          <a href="https://github.com/Joy-Majumder" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Joy Majumdar</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-bottom">
        <p>&copy; 2026 BurnLink. Share files. Encrypted. Ephemeral.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
